r)\n      Go-Pro and drone photographer and enjoys golf, traveling, and the Ohio State Buckeyes.\n"}],["preinheimer",{"name":"Paul Reinheimer","twitter":"preinheimer","github":"preinheimer","description":"      Paul has been programming since his mother gave him a book of\n      games for the Commodore 64 then \"lost\" the disk. His hobbies\n      include making things run faster, baking, photography, and reading.\n"}],["folley",{"name":"Folley Ogundele","github":"folley-ogundele","description":"      Before Stripe, Folley worked in business development at American Express\n      and IBM. He grew up in London, by way of Nigeria, and holds an MBA from\n      Imperial College London. Outside of work he enjoys American football,\n      karate and spending time with his young family.\n"}],["jieren",{"name":"Jieren Chen","twitter":"jierenchen","github":"gukjoon","description":"      Jieren is from Baltimore. Yes, he has seen the Wire. No, he has not lived the Wire.\n"}],["deirdre",{"name":"Deirdre Mullen","github":"deirdremullen","description":"      Deirdre is a Chicago native who studied Accounting and Finance\n      at Indiana University. Prior to joining Stripe's Finance team,\n      she worked at PwC and Thrillist Media Group in NYC.\n"}],["greg",{"name":"Greg Cooper","twitter":"awfy","github":"Awfy","description":"      Greg designs for Stripe. On the side he practices Jack Peñate's foot shuffle.\n"}],["meredith",{"name":"Meredith Colton Hazy","github":"meredithcoltonhazy","twitter":"cash","description":"      Prior to Stripe, Meredith worked on the revenue team at Twitter.\n      She studied English literature and political science at Stanford.\n"}],["karla",{"name":"Karla Burnett","twitter":"tetrakazi","github":"tetrakai","description":"      Karla is from Sydney originally, but ironically loves skiing and snow\n      boarding. When there's no snow around, she enjoys orienteering, cycling,\n      and dabbling in languages.\n"}],["mtowber",{"name":"Mike Towber","t